<h1>Thanks for your author proposal!</h1>

<p>Hi <%= @proposal.submitter_name || "there" %>,</p>

<p>
  We've received your proposal to improve author information on ChooseRuby. Your proposal has been assigned ID #<%= @proposal.id %>.
</p>

<% if @proposal.new_author_proposal? %>
  <p><strong>New Author Proposal:</strong> <%= @proposal.author_name %></p>
<% elsif @author.present? %>
  <p><strong>Author:</strong> <%= @author.name %></p>
<% end %>

<p><strong>What you proposed:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <% if @proposal.has_resource_proposal? %>
    <li>Resource suggestion: <%= @proposal.original_resource_url || @proposal.resource_url %></li>
  <% end %>
  <% if @proposal.has_link_updates? %>
    <li>Link updates (<%= @proposal.link_updates.keys.size %> changes)</li>
  <% end %>
  <% if @proposal.has_bio_changes? %>
    <li>
      <% if @proposal.bio_text.present? && @proposal.description_text.present? %>
        Bio and description updates
      <% elsif @proposal.bio_text.present? %>
        Bio update
      <% else %>
        Description update
      <% end %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>
  Our editorial team reviews every proposal to ensure quality and accuracy. You can expect an update within the next few business days.
</p>

<p>
  If we have any questions, we'll reach out to <%= @proposal.submitter_email %>.
</p>

<p>
  In the meantime, feel free to explore the latest additions on <%= link_to "chooseruby.com", root_url %>.
</p>

<p>â€” The ChooseRuby team</p>
